data.description: This great 2 story home has recently been lovingly updated with Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, new kitchen and baths.   The main living space is open and spacious.  Shiplap was added to the living room wall to showcase your flat screen TV.  The updated kitchen will be a joy to cook in.  The fridge also has a shiplap surround.  A large master bedroom or den is downstairs along with a mudroom and half bath.  Upstairs you will find 2 nice sized bedrooms with deep closets and a hall bath.   Out back you will find a brick patio, large storage shed and room for a garden.  The back yard is completely fenced in with vinyl fencing.   Close to all the town of Denton offers.
